{"heading":"Jesus came to suffer death and save men—He came to make reconciliation for the sins of the people.","number":2,"verseCount":18,"verses":[[1,["Therefore we ought to give the more ",["earnest",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Zeal","tg/zeal"],"."]]]," ",["heed",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 21:4","dc-testament/dc/21.4"],"."]]]," to the things which we have heard, lest at any time we should let ",["them",["clarity-word"]]," slip."]],[2,["For if the word spoken by angels was steadfast, and every transgression and ",["disobedience",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Disobedience","tg/disobedience"],"."]]]," received a ",["just",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Justice of","tg/god-justice-of"],"."]]]," recompence of reward;"]],[3,["How shall we ",["escape",["study-note-ref","a",[["Heb. 10:29","nt/heb/10.29"],"; ",["12:25","nt/heb/12.25"],"."]]],", if we neglect so great salvation; which at the first began to be spoken by the Lord, and was confirmed unto us by them that heard ",["him;",["clarity-word"]]]],[4,["God also bearing ",["them",["clarity-word"]]," witness, both with ",["signs",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 5:12 (12–23)","nt/acts/5.12"],". ",["TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of","tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"],"; ",["Symbolism","tg/symbolism"],"."]]]," and ",["wonders",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Miracle","tg/miracle"],"."]]],", and with divers miracles, and gifts of the Holy Ghost, according to his own ",["will",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG God, Will of","tg/god-will-of"],"."]]],"?"]],[5,["For unto the angels hath he not put in subjection the world to come, whereof we speak."]],[6,["But one in a certain place testified, saying, What is ",["man",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 8:4 (4–6)","ot/ps/8.4"],"."]]],", that thou art mindful of him? or the son of man, that thou visitest him?"]],[7,["Thou madest him a little lower than the ",["angels",["study-note-ref","a",["HEB gods; GR angels."]]],"; thou crownedst him with glory and honour, and didst set him over the works of thy hands:"]],[8,["Thou hast put all things in subjection under his ",["feet",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 28:18","nt/matt/28.18"],"; ",["1 Cor. 15:25","nt/1-cor/15.25"],"; ",["Eph. 1:22","nt/eph/1.22"],"."]]],". For in that he put all in subjection under him, he left nothing ",["that is",["clarity-word"]]," not put under him. But now we see not yet all things put under him."]],[9,["But we see Jesus, who was made a little ",["lower",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Condescension of","tg/jesus-christ-condescension-of"],"."]]]," than the ",["angels",["study-note-ref","b",[["Philip. 2:7 (7–9)","nt/philip/2.7"],"."]]]," ",["for",["study-note-ref","c",["GR through."]]]," the suffering of ",["death",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Jesus Christ, Death of","tg/jesus-christ-death-of"],"."]]],", ",["crowned",["study-note-ref","e",[["Acts 2:33","nt/acts/2.33"],"."]]]," with glory and honour; that he by the ",["grace",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Grace","tg/grace"],"."]]]," of God should taste ",["death",["study-note-ref","g",[["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"."]]]," for every man."]],[10,["For ",["it became him",["study-note-ref","a",["GR it was fitting, suitable, proper for Him."]]],", for whom ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," all things, and by whom ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," all ",["things",["study-note-ref","b",[["Col. 1:16 (13–19)","nt/col/1.16"],"."]]],", in bringing many sons unto glory, to make the ",["captain",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Jesus Christ, Messiah","tg/jesus-christ-messiah"],"."]]]," of their salvation ",["perfect",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Perfection","tg/perfection"],"."]]]," through sufferings."]],[11,["For both he that sanctifieth and they who are ",["sanctified",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Sanctification","tg/sanctification"],"."]]]," ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," all of ",["one",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Unity","tg/unity"],"."]]],": for which cause he is not ashamed to call them ",["brethren",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Brotherhood and Sisterhood","tg/brotherhood-and-sisterhood"],"."]]],","]],[12,["Saying, I will declare thy ",["name",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 22:22","ot/ps/22.22"],"."]]]," unto my brethren, in the midst of the church will I sing praise unto thee."]],[13,["And again, I will put my ",["trust",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 18:2","ot/ps/18.2"],"."]]]," in him. And again, Behold I and the children which God hath given me."]],[14,[["Forasmuch then as",["study-note-ref","a",["GR Since."]]]," the children are partakers of ",["flesh and blood",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Flesh and Blood","tg/flesh-and-blood"],"."]]],", he also himself likewise took part of the same; that through death he might ",["destroy",["study-note-ref","c",[["Gen. 3:15","ot/gen/3.15"],"."]]]," him that had the power of ",["death",["study-note-ref","d",[["2 Tim. 1:10","nt/2-tim/1.10"],". ",["TG Redemption","tg/redemption"],"."]]],", that is, the ",["devil",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Devil","tg/devil"],"."]]],";"]],[15,["And deliver them who through ",["",1523],"fear of death were all their lifetime subject to ",["bondage",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Bondage, Spiritual","tg/bondage-spiritual"],"; ",["Law of Moses","tg/law-of-moses"],"."]]],"."]],[16,["For verily he took not on ",["him the nature of",["clarity-word"]]," ",["angels",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Angels","tg/angels"],"."]]],"; but he took on ",["him",["clarity-word"]]," the ",["seed of Abraham",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Seed of Abraham","tg/seed-of-abraham"],"."]]],"."]],[17,["Wherefore in all things it behoved him to be made like unto ",["his",["clarity-word"]]," brethren, that he might be a merciful and faithful high priest in things ",["pertaining",["clarity-word"]]," to God, to make ",["reconciliation",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Redeemer","tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"],"; ",["Reconciliation","tg/reconciliation"],"."]]]," for the sins of the people."]],[18,["For in that he himself hath suffered being ",["tempted",["stud